        Last month Scapia raised <strong>$63M to become AI-first and reach the next India</strong>. Those travellers are not seasoned flyers chasing forex perks. <span class="hl">They travel for faith, and many are about to take a first flight.</span> Three waypoints, one companion, twelve months.
      </p>
