          <span class="legend"><span class="pin"></span> AI products shipped <b>→ Waypoint 03</b></span>
          <span class="legend"><span class="pin"></span> Sequencing, not sprawl <b>→ the whole map</b></span>
        </div>
        <div class="carto-avail">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
          <p><strong>Available immediately, no notice period.</strong> A company that just raised $63M to reach the next India cannot afford a quarter on a slow hiring cycle. I can start walking the route in week one.</p>
        </div>
